  <Fragment slot="intro">
    <p>That grinding or squealing noise from your LG dryer usually means the drum bearing is worn out. Our technicians replace drum bearings daily across LA County — it's one of the most common repairs on DLGX and DLEX models after 5-7 years of regular use. The bearing sits at the rear of the drum and supports the entire weight of your clothes during rotation.</p>
